the Dinosaur. For some reason his men tended to have a dinosaur motif
to them.&quot; CALIBER shrugged slightly. &quot;If he still has the ship, it
might be in that jungle area.&quot;

ELDER nodded, &quot;It is certainly big enough to hold his ship.&quot;

&quot;That jungle will eventually be large enough to encompass several
conntries in what will be later known as Central America.&quot; LEGACY said
