energy signature. It has the affect of blocking standard comlink
signals as well as inhibiting scanning beams.&quot;

ELDER furrowed his brow as if trying to remember something, then he
shook his head. &quot;A ship could bve in there and hidden well, but I have
been watching for quite some time now. I don&#39;t have any record of a
ship as large as the Dinsaur is reputed to be landing on Earth.&quot;

As they talked LEO PRIME walked into the room, &quot;Alright men strap on
your gear and let&#39;s get ready.&quot;

